@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_hqlspx(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = ((v1 - v0) + wp.cos((tmp + 0.47 - v0 + 0.13)))
    v1 = wp.sin(((v2 + 0.22 * v1 + 0.54) + wp.sin(v2 + 0.96)))
    v0 = (0.42 / v1)
    data[tid] = v0
